  "page_title": "SMC_CAMBounds (FB)",
  "text": "\nFUNCTION_BLOCK SMC_CAMBounds\nThis function block calculates the minimum/maximum position and an estimate of\nthe minimum/maximum velocity and acceleration values of the slave being coupled\nin absolute mode to a master, which is moved according to a prescribed maximum\nvelocity and acceleration/deceleration.\nThis module is especially helpful when a cam disc is created and modified in\nonline mode and the observance of the maximum values have to be checked in advance.\nNote: The minimum/maximum velocity and acceleration values are estimates\nof lower/upper bounds which do not necessarily have to be reached.\n",
